publicDeepCopyBytes(bytes,bytes).details: Performs a deep copy of a byte array onto another byte array of greater than or equal length.

params.dest: Byte array that will be overwritten with source bytes.
params.source: Byte array to copy onto dest bytes.

publicEquals(bytes,bytes).details: Tests equality of two byte arrays.
publicEquals(bytes,bytes).return: True if arrays are the same. False otherwise.

publicPopLast20Bytes(bytes).details: Pops the last 20 bytes off of a byte array by modifying its length.

params.b: Byte array that will be modified.

publicPopLast20Bytes(bytes).return: The 20 byte address that was popped off.

publicPopLastByte(bytes).details: Pops the last byte off of a byte array by modifying its length.

params.b: Byte array that will be modified.

publicPopLastByte(bytes).return: The byte that was popped off.

publicReadAddress(bytes,uint256).details: Reads an address from a position in a byte array.

params.index: Index in byte array of address.

params.b: Byte array containing a bytes32 value.

publicReadBytes4(bytes,uint256).details: Reads an unpadded bytes4 value from a position in a byte array.

params.b: Byte array containing a bytes4 value.
